<div class="epk-section">
    <h2>Bio</h2>
    <div class="epk-bio-box">
        <p class="epk-bio-text" id="epk-bio-content">SDSP is a Toronto-based high-volume, high-energy, indie band performing
            original music since mid-2025. Our sound blends post-punk, grunge, and garage rock. We draw inspiration from bands like
            DFA 1979, Nine Inch Nails, The Black Keys, and The White Stripes. We distinguish our heavy, riff-driven songs by
            incorporating unexpected blues elements, specifically harmonica and banjo, to create a fun, engaging, and high-energy
            live show.</p>
